sectionsArray.md:
Discount = Original Price \times \frac{Discount\%}{100}
- Original Price: The initial cost of the item
- Discount\%: The percentage discount offered
Tax = Price \times \frac{Tax\%}{100}
- Price: The cost after discount
- Tax\%: The percentage of sales tax
Tip = Meal Cost \times \frac{Tip\%}{100}
- Meal Cost: The total cost of the meal
- Tip\%: The percentage tip you wish to leave

